  "content": "<p>The problem sets and solutions from 2006 are useful as study materials. The solutions files are courtesy of students from that class, Xiaoguang Ma and Sawyer Tabony, and are used with permission.</p>\n<p><table>\n\n<thead>\n\n<tr>\n\n<th>\n\nASSIGNMENTS\n</th>\n\n<th>\n\nSOLUTIONS\n</th>\n</p>\n</tr>\n\n<p></thead>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td>\n\nProblem set 1 (<a href=\"/courses/18-100b-analysis-i-fall-2010/resources/mit18_100bf10_pset1-1/\">PDF</a>)\n</td>\n\n<td>\n\n(<a href=\"/courses/18-100b-analysis-i-fall-2010/resources/mit18_100bf10_pset1sol/\">PDF</a>)\n</td>\n</p>\n<p></tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td>\n\nProblem set 2 (<a href=\"/courses/18-100b-analysis-i-fall-2010/resources/mit18_100bf10_pset2-1/\">PDF</a>)\n</td>\n\n<td>\n\n(<a href=\"/courses/18-100b-analysis-i-fall-2010/resources/mit18_100bf10_pset2sol/\">PDF</a>)\n</td>\n</p>\n<p></tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td>\n\nProblem set 3 (<a href=\"/courses/18-100b-analysis-i-fall-2010/resources/mit18_100bf10_pset3-1/\">PDF</a>)\n</td>\n\n<td>\n\n(<a href=\"/courses/18-100b-analysis-i-fall-2010/resources/mit18_100bf10_pset3sol/\">PDF</a>)\n</td>\n</p>\n<p></tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td>\n\nProblem set 4 (<a href=\"/courses/18-100b-analysis-i-fall-2010/resources/mit18_100bf10_pset4-1/\">PDF</a>)\n</td>\n\n<td>\n\n(<a href=\"/courses/18-100b-analysis-i-fall-2010/resources/mit18_100bf10_pset4sol/\">PDF</a>)\n</td>\n</p>\n<p></tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td>\n\nProblem set 5 (<a href=\"/courses/18-100b-analysis-i-fall-2010/resources/mit18_100bf10_pset5-1/\">PDF</a>)\n</td>\n\n<td>\n\n(<a href=\"/courses/18-100b-analysis-i-fall-2010/resources/mit18_100bf10_pset5sol/\">PDF</a>)\n</td>\n</p>\n<p></tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td>\n\nProblem set 6 (<a href=\"/courses/18-100b-analysis-i-fall-2010/resources/mit18_100bf10_pset6-1/\">PDF</a>)\n</td>\n\n<td>\n\n(<a href=\"/courses/18-100b-analysis-i-fall-2010/resources/mit18_100bf10_pset6sol/\">PDF</a>)\n</td>\n</p>\n<p></tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td>\n\nProblem set 7 (<a href=\"/courses/18-100b-analysis-i-fall-2010/resources/mit18_10